<h2>colourvision: Colour Vision Models</h2>
<p>Colour vision models, colour spaces and colour thresholds. Provides flexibility to build user-defined colour vision models for n number of photoreceptor types. Also includes Vorobyev &amp; Osorio (1998) Receptor Noise Limited models, Chittka (1992) colour hexagon, and Endler &amp; Mielke (2005) model. Models have been extended to accept any number of photoreceptor types. </p>
